00:00:59.980 --> 00:01:02.260
Chen Wenbin, have you lost your mind?

00:01:03.020 --> 00:01:04.300
The ledger's with Zhou Nian.

00:01:05.220 --> 00:01:06.140
It's a fake.

00:01:06.380 --> 00:01:08.140
It's a trap set by Wang Penghui.

00:01:13.820 --> 00:01:15.820
It's too dangerous for you
to enter the Wang family now.

00:01:15.900 --> 00:01:17.860
I can help you with what you need to do.

00:01:17.860 --> 00:01:19.900
Wang Penghui already suspects you.

00:01:20.020 --> 00:01:20.900
Suspects what?

00:01:21.620 --> 00:01:22.660
Don't you realize how you're acting now

00:01:22.660 --> 00:01:24.220
is causing trouble for others?

00:01:24.220 --> 00:01:25.900
You think you're so clever, is that it?

00:01:25.940 --> 00:01:28.060
You'd even risk your marriage

00:01:28.060 --> 00:01:29.460
just to get into the Wang family?

00:01:30.260 --> 00:01:32.740
Liu Rumeng, are you insane?

00:01:33.140 --> 00:01:33.940
Yes.

00:01:37.100 --> 00:01:37.940
I'm desperate for revenge,

00:01:37.940 --> 00:01:39.420
so desperate I've gone mad.

00:01:39.540 --> 00:01:41.020
Wang Penghui suspects you, too.

00:01:41.260 --> 00:01:42.660
Do you think putting on a lovesick act

00:01:42.660 --> 00:01:44.460
in front of all those people

00:01:44.700 --> 00:01:46.100
actually helps me?

00:01:47.780 --> 00:01:48.940
What I want to do,

00:01:49.100 --> 00:01:50.220
and who I choose to marry,

00:01:50.580 --> 00:01:51.940
is my own business.

00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:54.700
I'm asking you...

00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:58.060
never to bother me again.

00:02:16.140 --> 00:02:16.940
Dad,

00:02:17.540 --> 00:02:18.860
there's something wrong with Liu Rumeng.

00:02:19.140 --> 00:02:20.620
We can't let her into the Wang family.

00:02:21.060 --> 00:02:23.700
Her relationship with Wenbin
is far from proper.

00:02:23.740 --> 00:02:25.460
If she really becomes your concubine,

00:02:25.500 --> 00:02:27.860
our family's reputation will be ruined.

00:02:28.220 --> 00:02:29.460
If I call off the engagement now,

00:02:30.100 --> 00:02:32.460
do you think we can walk away unscathed?

00:02:32.980 --> 00:02:34.740
Can't you use your head?

00:02:38.060 --> 00:02:40.860
There's one thing I don't get.

00:02:43.460 --> 00:02:44.340
Just what method

00:02:44.340 --> 00:02:46.460
did Liu Rumeng use

00:02:47.140 --> 00:02:48.180
to make Chen Wenbin

00:02:48.180 --> 00:02:50.300
so devoted to her?

00:02:50.860 --> 00:02:51.660
Dad,

00:02:51.980 --> 00:02:52.700
this woman

00:02:52.700 --> 00:02:54.500
flirts with men everywhere.

00:02:54.500 --> 00:02:55.780
- So she...
- Does it matter?

00:02:56.540 --> 00:02:58.900
If you had even half of her cunning,

00:02:59.180 --> 00:03:00.700
Chen Wenbin would have...

00:03:03.060 --> 00:03:03.860
Forget it.

00:03:04.220 --> 00:03:05.740
I can't even be bothered to scold you.

00:03:06.740 --> 00:03:07.540
Sweetheart,

00:03:09.060 --> 00:03:10.660
have you ever seriously considered

00:03:10.660 --> 00:03:11.980
why I do these things

00:03:11.980 --> 00:03:13.300
day after day?

00:03:14.260 --> 00:03:15.420
If our Wang family

00:03:15.420 --> 00:03:17.220
has the Chen family's support,

00:03:17.540 --> 00:03:20.260
let alone returning
to the Chamber of Commerce,

00:03:20.580 --> 00:03:23.060
even the position
of Chamber President

00:03:24.140 --> 00:03:26.300
will be within my grasp.

00:03:26.900 --> 00:03:28.420
You saw it yourself today.

00:03:29.020 --> 00:03:30.500
That scumbag Li

00:03:30.620 --> 00:03:32.740
humiliated me in front of everyone.

00:03:37.900 --> 00:03:39.020
It shouldn't be too difficult, actually.

00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:41.020
Remember when we were playing cards
that night?

00:03:42.420 --> 00:03:44.140
Mr. Li could barely

00:03:44.940 --> 00:03:46.820
take his eyes off Liu Rumeng.

00:03:54.100 --> 00:03:54.900
Excuse me.

00:04:04.300 --> 00:04:06.260
You're finally showing some cleverness.

00:04:08.100 --> 00:04:09.100
Liu Rumeng,

00:04:09.460 --> 00:04:10.540
this is the price you pay

00:04:10.540 --> 00:04:12.300
for messing with Wenbin.

00:04:22.580 --> 00:04:23.460
You're injured?

00:04:25.660 --> 00:04:27.740
I heard all the guests talking today

00:04:28.260 --> 00:04:30.620
about the Wang family's concubine
and you, Marshal Chen.

00:04:31.180 --> 00:04:32.820
The two of you were all over each other.

00:04:32.900 --> 00:04:34.420
You had me, a reporter, play the thief.

00:04:36.740 --> 00:04:37.860
With the stir you caused today,

00:04:38.260 --> 00:04:40.460
all of Song City is buzzing.

00:04:41.100 --> 00:04:42.260
You saved her, yes.

00:04:42.660 --> 00:04:44.260
But how do you plan
to deal with the aftermath?

00:04:45.260 --> 00:04:46.180
You thought you couldn't

00:04:46.620 --> 00:04:48.260
stop Liu Rumeng?

00:04:49.220 --> 00:04:50.860
So you caused the scandal

00:04:51.220 --> 00:04:52.460
to make Wang Penghui

00:04:52.500 --> 00:04:54.100
give up on marrying her, right?

00:04:58.300 --> 00:04:59.820
It is the only way to stop her

00:05:01.300 --> 00:05:02.700
from marrying into the Wang family.

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:19.600
[Blycher Hotel]

00:05:55.620 --> 00:05:56.660
What are you doing?

00:05:57.940 --> 00:05:59.140
I have everything arranged.

00:06:00.180 --> 00:06:00.900
If you agree,

00:06:00.900 --> 00:06:02.140
I'll take you away right now.

00:06:03.220 --> 00:06:05.060
I've made myself perfectly clear.

00:06:05.540 --> 00:06:07.420
Even if this path leads me to heck,

00:06:08.540 --> 00:06:09.500
