00:07:42.140 --> 00:07:43.940
I cut my hand

00:07:44.940 --> 00:07:46.340
while changing into the wedding gown.

00:07:54.980 --> 00:07:55.780
Come here.

00:08:09.700 --> 00:08:10.860
It seems beautiful people

00:08:10.860 --> 00:08:12.660
should wear beautiful clothes.

00:08:13.660 --> 00:08:14.980
On our wedding day,

00:08:15.580 --> 00:08:16.660
