00:09:50.620 --> 00:09:52.580
And you still have feelings for her?

00:09:52.980 --> 00:09:54.540
Aren't you ashamed?

00:09:56.700 --> 00:09:58.260
This place is nice.

00:10:06.380 --> 00:10:08.180
I must have Chen Wenbin.

00:10:08.540 --> 00:10:10.460
I can't let my father down.

00:10:11.660 --> 00:10:13.300
Miss Wang, the incense burner
you prepared

00:10:13.300 --> 00:10:15.100
